dct_title_s: Map of the City of New York
dct_description_sm: Cadastral map. Covers Manhattan, New York (N.Y.) and adjacent parts of the Bronx, New York (N.Y.) Shows existing and proposed streets, railroads, ferries, cemeteries, parks. Also shows former property and lot lines, property owners' names and a few buildings. Shows depths by soundings. Oriented with north toward the upper left.
